Message: I have $250 incentive ad credits in my account. But it's still giving warning "Your account needs a valid payment method before your ad can be reviewed and delivered. Add payment method."

It sounds like you need to add a valid payment method to your account even if you have ad credits. Ad credits are always used before your primary payment method, but having a valid credit card on file is still required. Hereâ€™s how you can add a payment method:
1. Access the Billing Section.
2. Click 'add payment method.'
3. Provide your credit card information and save.
For more details, you can check out our Billing Guide here: [Billing Guide](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/17821681919757-Billing-Guide).
